ing: 2 (15 ounce) cans cannellini beans, drained and rinsed
des: "This yummy and flavorful soup really brings out the flavor of the kale. Enjoy with some homemade cornbread on a cold night!"
ins: Combine the chicken broth, vegetable broth, water, chicken, cannellini beans, potatoes, pepper, salt, oregano, and garlic powder in a large pot; bring to a boil; reduce heat to medium-high and cook until the potatoes are fork-tender, about 15 minutes. Add the kale and cook another 5 minutes; serve.
